Items.Name: Romklao Automation Co Ltd
Items.Description:
Romklao Automation are the solution provider for Control valves and On/off valves in Pulp & Paper industry including other related industrial applications. Our engineered valve product lines include SOMAS ball segment, ball and butterfly valves (Sweden), A+R ball valves (Germany), OMC globe control valves (Italy), Actuatech pneumatic scotch-yoke actuator (Italy) and ABB smart positioner (Germany) which are basically designed for use in the paper & pulp industry and naturally adapted to the specific demands of this industry. We have been experiencing in providing control valve packages for project bidding for many Pulp & Paper mills. Our specially designed and custom-made product packages meet or even exceed customer, specific requirements.

Romklao Automation have Sales staff with over 9-year experience in Pulp & Paper industry and well-trained
and pernanent skilled service staff to serve our customers when needed. Our workshop have well-equipped facilities and equipment necessary to perform valve repair, automation, calibration and testing. We follow and comply to the international standards of pressure testing, e.g. IEC534-4, ANSI FCI 70-2,1505208, API 598 etc.

Romklao Automation sales office/workshop is located on Romklao Rd., Bangkok (Approximately 15 minutes by car from Suvarnabhumi Airport and Motorway).
